name: Public Health Statistics - Preterm births in Chicago, by year, 1999 – 2009
description: This dataset contains the annual number of preterm births and the percent of total births these preterm births represent, with corresponding 95% confidence intervals, by Chicago community area, for the years 1999 – 2009.  See the full dataset description for more information: http://bit.ly/M7AyBL
